rComments: The exams were fairly easy, the french was poor and hard to understand at points, explanations were not always clear and his slides lacked detail.

Took this class in French, expected a French prof. This prof's French is terrible, should've just taken the course in English. You have to attend classes as  his lectures are long, and his slides are very empty. Midterm exams are not that long, but the content is tough. Wish he would've explained things better.

Super interesting content, however his french is not very good, and he has a hard time communicating the content in an efficient way. His slides also lack the necessary information, so it's hard to know what to study. Exams are pretty easy, but there's so much content, it's hard to do well.

His French isn't the best, but the explanation is really good! Although, I think you need to have a specific character to actually like this guy. I think I'm the only one who actually enjoys his teaching   The subjects are super interesting, and you really need to go to class cause not all the info are on the slides
